channel.title: Help! cant find ip address! i have team viewer
channel.description: i cant find the port and ip adress thing where i put my ip address!!! help please u can teamviewer me! its for client.java

item.title: Help! cant find ip address! i have team viewer
item.dc:creator: @Owner_Zack_of_Pwnage Owner Zack of PwnageScape
item.description:
@Owner_Zack_of_Pwnage wrote:

cluter123:

you know when u have to put it the ip address for the client that way people can connect to ur ip, i need to know where it is, i tried the 0.0 thing and i need help!!!

First of all, look in the client folder. Client.java there.
Then, search for “Server”, “no-ip”, or “127.0.0.1”. If you find any of these, change the IP Address after the “=” sign, to your no-ip or whatever. Then compile.
